    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beans are lightly charred, remove the pan from the heat and add your<strong> cooked brown long grain rice</strong> and the <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and cook for 3-4 min, stirring frequently, or until the rice is warmed through and the spinach has wilted</p><p>Once wilted, add the <strong>remaining tamari soy sauce</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>brown rice & greens</strong></p>",
