    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer to a plate and remove the pan from the heat (reserve the pan!)</p><p>Add the <strong>red Thai curry stock</strong> to the reserved pan</p><p>Tip: Be careful when adding the stock to the pan, it may splash!</p><p>Return the pan to a medium heat and cook for 2-3 min or until thickened<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>red Thai curry sauce</strong></p>",
